thread.title: Turkish central bank leaves main interest rate unchanged
thread.title_full: Turkish central bank leaves main interest rate unchanged | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: Turkish central bank leaves main interest rate unchanged
text:
ISTANBUL, July 23 Turkey's central bank left its benchmark one-week repo rate unchanged at 7.5 percent on Thursday as a recent drop in food prices took pressure off inflation and global liquidity remained ample.
All 16 economists polled by Reuters had expected key interest rates to be left on hold. (Writing by Daren Butler ; Editing by David Dolan , Larry King)
